Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等‧‧‧暫停!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不會再讓你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:15.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 命中注定要跟我結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:17.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人是要跟帕皮結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:20.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有我才配當主公的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主公!                          主人!                       Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:28.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結‧‧‧結婚什麼的 會什麼會變成這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:52.72,標題,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「危險狀況的日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好 接下來讓我們複習一下他種族間交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:07.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,首先是第一條 人類和他種族不得互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:08.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,接下來是第二條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,禁止在無寄宿家庭人員陪同下外出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最後是第三條 這是最為重要的一條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:18.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在寄宿家庭中留學生前輩最偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以妳們都要聽我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要擅自修改法案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.63,TOP-2,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,580)}笨蛋也能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:25.28,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要被騙了! 帕皮!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好了 都明白了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷亞同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:33.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吵死了! 他種族間交流法我早就記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:34.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:39.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐要妳把寄宿家庭的申請資料填好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人類和他種族間不得互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.55,MonMusu-flashback,brume0425,0,0,0,,得為米亞準備洗澡水才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我沒想到賽蕾雅正在裡面洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒‧‧‧沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因‧‧‧因為我去晨跑出了很多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要是我鎖上門就不會發生這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊的 我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊! Darling真是的 老愛護著珊卓雷亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:22.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷亞快去填寄宿家庭的申請資料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 半人馬族太野蠻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過是裸體被看到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳自己還不是一樣 真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我聽墨須小姐說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳害主公的肩膀脫臼了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個是我無法抑制自己個感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:41.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,比起這個 主公可是為了保護我迎向壞人的兇器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是 Darling為了我收拾了那些不良份子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.87,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,他保護我的時候更加勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧妳們兩個適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:00.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他種族亂交法太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,腦袋好熱 好想洗冷水澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那就去浴室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人我們一起去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦‧‧‧那讓米亞或讓賽蕾雅‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可是和Darling一起洗過澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我被主公揉‧‧‧揉過胸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那算什麼‧‧‧真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:22.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好涼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳給我等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐幫妳準備了泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼是學校泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為只有這個尺寸合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可是 我這樣的手沒有辦法換
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,洞在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為我還不習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不知道是哪一個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到深處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍微‧‧‧有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,接下來把腳穿進另一邊的洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我看不見 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:08.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍微有一點癢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最後把手穿過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,翅膀擋著穿不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒問題的 泳裝彈性很強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抱歉 我讓頭腦冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳喜歡怎麼玩都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那帕皮也讓頭腦冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣就像是海獺父女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮覺得是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:57.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果我有哥哥 感覺就像主人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像我?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為因為 你會跟我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我做錯事也會溫柔的提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還會誇獎我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:11.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為哈耳庇厄族只有女生 所以不懂哥哥是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:15.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但我從以前就很橦憬 現在我非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛‧‧‧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:21.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當我是哥哥的話倒也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以讓我們兄妹好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛才被主人碰到胸部時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我突然心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以讓我感受更多心跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,兄妹才不會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還要抵抗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.80,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡! 可惡! 可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那只好我就來硬的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 本來以為妳是小孩子就沒管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然和我同年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此就不能允許妳恣意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒辦法動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:58.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來 主公 坐在我背上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦? 嗯‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,給我等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們兩個居然偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐馬上就要來拿資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅去填資料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不然‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,臭馬女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在過一段時間 帕皮頭腦也會冷靜下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊吧 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,坐在賽蕾雅背上吹風衣服也乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓能請你把手放開嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對‧‧‧對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕不是故意的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:51.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作為侍奉主公的人這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是奉主公什麼的 太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,才不誇張!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:01.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吾等半人馬是把對主公的忠誠放在第一的高貴戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以才會找甘願侍奉的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我的父親‧祖父‧曾祖父代代都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我作為一名女人前 我還是個騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這就是吾等種族的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說誇張什麼的‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是什麼 替身?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡畢竟是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,半人馬族的文化雖然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:29.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過稍微放鬆一下也不壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這種事‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好不容易通過他種族間交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳不就是為此而來 有什麼想做的事情嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想做的‧‧‧事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.46,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦‧‧‧怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那個 不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,手‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,手?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:58.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想試著牽‧‧‧手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:58.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:08:59.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:03.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到目前為止握過的東西 就只有劍跟弓而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:09.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果是人類社會的女孩 都會想這樣做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有什麼特別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:16.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不是 身為侍奉主公人的人是不配身份的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛剛的就當我沒說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是這種感覺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:35.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個 賽蕾雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我自己都不知道我現在是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都說不要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼啊? 帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為妳要我把妳放下來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可沒說把我丟下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們兩個為什麼在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳自己不是說禁止單獨行動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不被發現就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這種歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓‧‧‧雷~雅~ ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧這是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這個臭馬女 為了調情把Darling擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這哪裡是高貴的半人馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,輪不到妳這復仇心重的蛇女說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再說誰是妳Darling啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳是在以主公的妻子自居嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那主人就歸帕皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,鳥翅膀給我閃開!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:40.98,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(522,304)}獸 耳 每 一 天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,獸耳~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那些孩子們‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:51.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此就用力量決定高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,等. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,住手‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:17.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什‧‧‧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人!   Darling!  主公!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀! 沒想到會打到Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖說是麻醉彈 吃了三發真虧你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哪裡沒事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這會變成責任問題的 所以請你保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,換作平常早就飛奔過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,盯~ ~ ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳們在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:55.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為‧‧‧我們擅作主張 所以才讓Darling遇到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作為侍奉主人之仁是我不稱職
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:07.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以‧‧‧從今後為了不給Darling添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家決定要努力忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,忍耐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:14.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯 帕皮不會拉著主人陪我玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不會再做不符合自身身份的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們在說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,確實妳們偶爾會做過頭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吵架也並不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:23.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這次最該道歉的人是墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有糾紛是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:34.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭的意義不就是為了跨越這些障礙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然寄宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我們就是家人了 不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:45.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以不用互相客氣和忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:47.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.95,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,那正好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,家人‧‧‧家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,把大家交給Darling君果然是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:03.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,其實最近有修正他種族間交流法的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:08.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖然就只是改一下細節而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:12.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,其中有一項是允許人類可以和他種族結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過現在正在尋找是否有可行的案例
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:18.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:23.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君你就和米亞‧帕皮‧賽蕾雅‧其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結婚吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔~物~娘 !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:43.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為‧‧‧為什麼突然說起結婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:46.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為隨著今後人類和他種族交流不斷深入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這件事將無法避免
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以你就做為先例‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是這個意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳突然叫我結婚讓我很傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也太亂來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳叫我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,加油之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就這麼隨便的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧怎麼這樣就要回去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為‧‧‧事情都辦完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼加油吧~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:24.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好像有什麼事忘了說?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛~算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,突然叫我結婚 她到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明說過出手的話要會被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不不‧‧‧我也沒打算要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖然被逼迫過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,每次都不知道忍的多辛苦‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我在說什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結婚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 你醒著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:02.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總覺得Darling很苦惱 所以很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:06.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個‧‧‧我在想你是不是討厭和我們結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧並不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是單方面被說 有點不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,並不是不願意結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛‧‧‧直接說就是那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:24.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我沒有跟女生交往過 還是個處男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來如此!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,並不是不願意結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:28.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就相信Darling一定會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:36.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為Darling非常溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:40.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我最喜歡Darling這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling你知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:47.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蛇的交尾是要持續一整晚的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像這樣全身互相糾纏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:57.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,互相將其身體的境界線融化再一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:07.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們也來融為一體吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.93,MonMusu-internal/narrator,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.48,MonMusu-internal/narrator,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖然平常卿卿我我 總是很黏人感覺‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.41,MonMusu-internal/narrator,brume0425,0,0,0,,但今晚該怎麼說呢 妖豔?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等等‧‧‧米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒事吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂 內褲 內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯~沒事~沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮要和主人結婚的所以沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼叫沒問題啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再說你知道結婚的意思嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:48.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就是交尾‧下蛋之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人的XX?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.64,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,太直接了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這種話不可以說!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼? 因為帕皮已經是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,也可以下蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:02.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當然可以交尾 所以沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:05.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,也可以和主人結婚的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.23,MonMusu-internal/narrator,brume0425,0,0,0,,連帕皮也是到底是什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.67,MonMusu-internal/narrator,brume0425,0,0,0,,就算提到結婚有關的事 變化也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主公 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來晚了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:22.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,得救了 賽蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總覺得大家的樣子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為今天是滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本能會被強烈的喚醒的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,滿月?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再加上結婚這個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經失去自我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就因為這種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,賽‧‧‧賽蕾雅妳沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:46.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當然! 我不會因為滿月就失去平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我已經跟主公宣示忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身體‧心‧都是主公的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因此 做什麼都可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這已經等同於結婚!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來~請隨意盡情的摸 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失去了! 妳的平常心早失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,直接來的話更好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 可以緊抱你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮也想抱緊主人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別想偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也想抱!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:30.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經完全出於本能 所以力量的分寸也不能掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,現在如果被抓住的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說不定‧‧‧會死! !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不會再讓你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling命中注定要和我結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人是要跟帕皮結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有我才配當主公的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,700)}主公!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,700)}主人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(1059,700)}Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我忘記說了 今晚是滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我知道  !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再這樣下去再婚禮之前就要先舉行葬禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,陷進去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有陷進去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都怪妳說了結婚以後 讓她們更興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧Darling君決定要跟誰結婚了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:24.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然還沒有得出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼可能得出結論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君今後該怎麼辦 和她們談過了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你該不會立即把自己關在房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:42.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不跟她們好好說清楚 她們會變得不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以大家才會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:49.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總之現在先想辦法讓她們頭腦冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎. . . 怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:52.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,附近有冰箱嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,用冰塊讓她們腦袋降溫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,, 這也太隨便‧‧‧.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,手機‧‧‧掉水裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐?  墨須小姐!  墨須小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了 !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:16.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不會再讓你跑了 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼了 Darling ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,全身濕淋淋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人!  主公!  Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎‧‧‧什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧番茄醬‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不知道能不能洗掉啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,700)}Darling   主人    主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 妳們冷靜下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,恢復原樣‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 快起來 天亮了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮和賽蕾雅也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:59.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?  Darling 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人你被誰打了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,昨天晚上發生什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒事!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,才怪‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:15.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,變成這樣是因為我優柔寡斷的態度造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為這樣讓大家感到不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:22.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,接下來我要把結論說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結論?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:29.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我今後會以結婚為前提和大家交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以‧‧‧那個‧‧‧什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:34.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還有‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,700)}Darling!                            主人!               主公!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:46.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,滿月之夜‧‧‧大家要早點睡覺‧‧‧
